#Text=I wear these on a daily basis  .  IMPLICIT I purchase because they are the only 6E leather on the market .  IMPLICIT I'm on my feet at work and I have to replace the insoles in about a month, as they compress and then my foot moves .  IMPLICIT

#Text=Wanted to love this shoe .  IMPLICIT Lots of support, light for zumba, but the fit was too small .  IMPLICIT I had to return, and am cautious about ordering the next size up .  IMPLICIT This is a disappointment, as NEW BALANCE shoes always fit so well .  IMPLICIT
#Text=These are classic grey 574 NB sneakers .  IMPLICIT Comfortable, durable, stylish in any casual setting or activity .  IMPLICIT A real can't-go-wrong purchase .  IMPLICIT

#Text=Gorgeous shoe—update of a classic design .  IMPLICIT Just too narrow for my 3E paws .  IMPLICIT @NB, please expand your line of wide sneaks .  IMPLICIT You've always been there for us !  IMPLICIT

#Text=Liked the look of the shoe, so I purchased it online .  IMPLICIT It's a comfortable, good looking shoe .  IMPLICIT Probably ok for a run, but will end up wearing it for casual use .  IMPLICIT NB runs a little small .  IMPLICIT I'm a 9, but even a 9 . 5D is a little snug .  IMPLICIT

#Text=I was so excited to receive these shoes but was surprised when they arrived and looked so different from the photo/description on the website .  IMPLICIT The N is NOT black, it is purplish and sparkly .  IMPLICIT Fine if that's your style, but was not what I was expecting so had to return .  IMPLICIT
#Text=These are super cute but run small .  IMPLICIT I order 2 pair in my normal size but this pair is cut smaller and too tight around the front of my foot ☹️ IMPLICIT

#Text=I have only worn them twice and I really like them .  IMPLICIT I like them so much that I bought a second pair but a size smaller and they came in the mail today .  IMPLICIT Went to a party Saturday night and got a lot of compliments .  IMPLICIT The colors don't match the picture though but I'm fine with that .  IMPLICIT

#Text=I love the look of this shoe, However, the width of this shoe has changed .  IMPLICIT I've purchased five of these shoes and the last two were both to narrow .  IMPLICIT Normally they are amazingly all day comfortable, and offer great support for weak ankles .  IMPLICIT
#Text=Great fit .  IMPLICIT Thank you New Balance for making a range of widths .  IMPLICIT

#Text=Great shoes !  IMPLICIT Love the style and comfort .  IMPLICIT This versatile shoe looks goods and feels even better !  IMPLICIT

#Text=The hiking boots feel true to size but just a little tight across the width of foot however the boot is leather so with time they should be broken in and stretch . #Text=The shoes take a little "breaking in", but are nice and well made .  IMPLICIT However, I ordered an 8 . 5, and it was bigger than other 8 . 5 shoes that i've bought in other brands .  IMPLICIT
